edBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:15:37.000Z","msg":"上次我老婆都係凌晨先起，去左急症同佢講呼吸困難等左3-4個字就有得睇"},{"pid":"bbf2f2b33758245e3a2b594684ab4627ad1ff96e","tid":38202,"uid":18741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"上次急証好快<br />\n由到醫院到啪支針<br />\n前後30分鐘搞掂<br />\n啪完支針會好眼訓<br />\n啪完要極速返屋企"},{"pid":"26cd70c4cf7ade6ee5e086285bae2bc3d839030d","tid":38202,"uid":28042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:33:06.000Z","msg":"Thanks 咁多位 去緊急症 <br />\n但我一條友去 話呼吸困難會唔會唔信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb4055d9219c7480ad3ce8b003209f5056bf1e0","tid":38202,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Thanks 咁多位 去緊急症 <br />\n但我一條友去 話呼吸困難會唔會唔信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去撚到醫院都有排等,我上次越生越大達,心口上頸都係,都等撚左粒半鐘先肯幫我打針.但打完半粒鐘就沉返"},{"pid":"0f1c18566f96524c9880f97d9a9f7a273ba24a63","tid":38202,"uid":15966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:45:30.000Z","msg":"風癱都會呼呼困難？我生左幾個月都無 因為我慢性?"},{"pid":"e1c3af4d6d5ded13e51b16e708bde49bc869cce5","tid":38202,"uid":47926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:46:58.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪食錯咩敏感呀<br />\n濕熱都會 試過連續出兩個月 最後睇中醫先搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7292cca440aa8051bb9aba69233ec28312a3d21c","tid":38202,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Thanks 咁多位 去緊急症 <br />\n但我一條友去 話呼吸困難會唔會唔信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢d野佢撚知你你扮似d就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過來人有呢個病差唔多十年好明白"},{"pid":"5763a60372f67e5ad89ad81e15c7395403f38fda","tid":38202,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T19:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風癱都會呼呼困難？我生左幾個月都無 因為我慢性?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n敏感急性過敏真係有可能呼吸困難<br />\n外國d咩花生敏感死都有類似case"},{"pid":"700b3a859e3328a7a99e5eb375e86ff7640854ac","tid":38202,"uid":53978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T20:18:20.000Z","msg":"呼吸困難都有得呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望一望你個樣度下個血氧都知你咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4d40454d846bd83ffa1bb6af72e74e80ea8b92","tid":38202,"uid":2734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T20:25:05.000Z","msg":"黃色藥丸好快控制住<br />\n不過我都試過2次睇急症"},{"pid":"0111fb1b481a0aef61ece7f385e79d5ce3a452ac","tid":38202,"uid":29717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T20:35:50.000Z","msg":"屋企有冇收鼻水藥？頂住先<br />\n醫院開敏感藥同我講其實係收鼻水藥"},{"pid":"e9dbdd5c2369ce5cac045f66f18fea9a9f4dfbb6","tid":38202,"uid":59546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T20:38:18.000Z","msg":"用殭狂碎幾分鐘 再用厚被焗返一陣就好返 利申細個呀媽幫我咁做 唔知得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}